1. *Zaustavio* sam auto na semaforu. (I stopped the car at the traffic light.)
2. Policajac me je *zaustavio* zbog prekoračenja brzine. (The police officer stopped me for speeding.)
3. Ne mogu da se setim ko me je *zaustavio* sinoć na ulici. (I can't remember who stopped me on the street last night.)
4. Uspela sam da *zaustavim* voz na vreme. (I managed to stop the train on time.)
5. Nisam mogao da *zaustavim* svoje misli. (I couldn't stop my thoughts.)
6. Moraćemo da *zaustavimo* gradnju zbog nedostatka materijala. (We'll have to stop the construction due to lack of materials.)
7. *Zaustavljajući* se pored reke, uživali smo u predivnom pogledu. (Stopping by the river, we enjoyed the beautiful view.)
8. Moramo *zaustaviti* rastuću inflaciju. (We have to stop the growing inflation.)